    <h2>Ideation and planning</h2>
    <p>WP Engine partnered with <a href="https://heyletsgo.co/">Hey Let's Go</a> and <a href="http://september.club/">September Club</a> to film and produce the documentary. Execution of the website should follow their editing style, typography, lower thirds, and other visually impactful queues from the film.</p>
    <p>We identified a clear set of goals for the website:</p>
